ft:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8a3fa24997f0af46fb9ff3fd7f95b8e9/6dd08/4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 59.786184210526315%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"文章\"\n        title=\"文章\"\n        src=\"/static/8a3fa24997f0af46fb9ff3fd7f95b8e9/799d3/4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8a3fa24997f0af46fb9ff3fd7f95b8e9/00d96/4.png 148w,\n/static/8a3fa24997f0af46fb9ff3fd7f95b8e9/0b23c/4.png 295w,\n/static/8a3fa24997f0af46fb9ff3fd7f95b8e9/799d3/4.png 590w,\n/static/8a3fa24997f0af46fb9ff3fd7f95b8e9/2a3d6/4.png 885w,\n/static/8a3fa24997f0af46fb9ff3fd7f95b8e9/ae92f/4.png 1180w,\n/static/8a3fa24997f0af46fb9ff3fd7f95b8e9/6dd08/4.png 1216w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5575aaff8ef271610c625b40b9b0517b/d81c9/5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 59.94318181818182%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"留言\"\n        title=\"留言\"\n        src=\"/static/5575aaff8ef271610c625b40b9b0517b/799d3/5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5575aaff8ef271610c625b40b9b0517b/00d96/5.png 148w,\n/static/5575aaff8ef271610c625b40b9b0517b/0b23c/5.png 295w,\n/static/5575aaff8ef271610c625b40b9b0517b/799d3/5.png 590w,\n/static/5575aaff8ef271610c625b40b9b0517b/2a3d6/5.png 885w,\n/static/5575aaff8ef271610c625b40b9b0517b/d81c9/5.png 1056w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h4>结语</h4>\n<p>工作是实现一个人价值的方式，但不是唯一的。人生的每一个阶段有每个阶段的诉求，有这个阶段具有的悲喜和忧愁，在默默承受这些成长的同时，应该为下一个阶段做好充足的准备。未来是不可预知的，你应该采取什么样的态度，这是值得思考的问题。</p>\n<h3>你好，2019</h3>\n<p>上部分写了一些当时的感想和工作上的总结。2019，渴望拥有新的变化，不论是职业或者状态。在人际交往上，希望可以和更多的人交流，以此提高自己的口语 (@.@)，因为平时练习口语的机会真的是太少了。</p>\n<h3>考试</h3>\n<p>本想指学习的，但为了区别以前理解的“学习”，还是用考试吧，这也比较符合实际环境。总结以下比较符合我的考试大概有这些：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>0</th>\n<th>名称</th>\n<th>说明</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>教师资格证 、 软考</td>\n<td>职业</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>IELTS</td>\n<td>语言</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>专业知识</td>\n<td>！！</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>考研</td>\n<td>升学</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>公务员</td>\n<td>职业</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>毕业时的初心是升学，会朝着这个方向努力，但如开头提到，就是为了升学，而不是其他什么。其间会面临很多现实的选择，那是正常的。</p>\n<p>以后会写有关备考的文章。</p>\n<p>…待续。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"2018的终章","los":"昆明•云南•中国","date":"2018年01月28日","description":""}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/2018年的终章/","previous":null,"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/前方的路/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"前方的路"}}}}}